    "client_msg_id": "3b2ca15d-726a-4ea8-b4d9-e960cc198c4b",
    "type": "message",
    "text": "The argument is that most of the toil and expertise required is for solving the purely incidental problems of software - the ones that have no bearing at all on the business, but are merely implementation details.",
