    "type": "message",
    "text": "… For now. At my last job, a savvy group of young, non-technical, fresh-out-of-college folks googled their way through administrating a Dynamics CRM deployment, and were able to create quite an amazing, custom-fit system, with no previous IT experience and very little help from the IT department. That wouldn’t have been possible 15 years ago, and I imagine even more will be possible in the future.",
